{"tid":1439430,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"財經界：和理非，不合作運動","createTime":"2019-08-10T06:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T11:30:15.000Z","uid":26619,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"09a55446bc02adcc2c43e2a99ac08756ba8d929b","tid":1439430,"uid":26619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:04:24.000Z","msg":"林鄭講move on 講經濟。<br />\n我地就從經濟層面，回應林鄭政府。<br />\n<br />\n2018香港政府從印花稅收入達1000億，<br />\n佔總收入16.5%。<br />\n印花稅通過由買賣樓到股票收入。<br />\n所以我們以減少買港股，<br />\n轉買美股，從而減少政府財政，<br />\n減少買入更多催淚彈、<br />\n橡膠子彈等殺人武器的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n如果無買股票，<br />\n也可以將強績金改成美股。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FR4p3oG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFR4p3oG.png&h=32c56189&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/research-publications/chinese/1718issf03-major-sources-of-government-revenue-20180302-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fresearch-publications%2Fchinese%2F1718issf03-major-sources-of-government-revenue-20180302-c.pdf&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68s3XW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=68b00aaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/research-publications/chinese/1718issf03-major-sources-of-government-revenue-20180302-c.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"b382fd2ded54f13f9af7c06fb7c7adabc6cc1295","tid":1439430,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:45:38.000Z","msg":"貿易戰經濟轉差浮面<br />\n<br />\n但入晒反送中數"},{"pid":"4b9a892afb598e24aea3ac267d67a69f5558434f","tid":1439430,"uid":40470,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:46:38.000Z","msg":"港股成交靠大戶撐起<br />\n<br />\n其實連登仔唔炒股你估人地真係會驚咩"},{"pid":"daa6981901ff294fbb32a8187993940deecb6bf9","tid":1439430,"uid":47558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b9a892afb598e24aea3ac267d67a69f5558434f","tid":1439430,"uid":40470,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:46:38.000Z","msg":"港股成交